OL,5,CCouncil bin strike continues
OL,7,FBins are overflowing and rubbish is
OL,8,Fscattered across the streets of South
OL,9,FTyneside as industrial action
OL,10,Fcontinues.
OL,12,FSouth Tyneside Council launched an
OL,13,Findependent investigation into
OL,14,Fgrievances raised by refuse
OL,15,Foperatives, which the GMB union say
OL,16,Fincluded claims of bullying and
OL,17,Fmismanagement, in June. The
OL,18,Finvestigation into the claims
OL,19,Fconcluded in November 2023.
