OL,7,FThe strike - which means the next
OL,8,Fcollection is 26 January - follows
OL,9,Fprevious action in November, December
OL,10,Fand earlier this month.
OL,12,FThe unions are warning of more strikes
OL,13,Fin the coming months, over what they
OL,14,Fsay is an "accumulation of years of
OL,15,Fintolerable working conditions".
