OL,7,FThe unions have said new housing has
OL,8,Fincreased the workload of refuse
OL,9,Fcollections, without extra staff or
OL,10,Fbin lorries, and allege they have been
OL,11,Fserved disciplinary notices for
OL,12,Fhelping elderly people while
OL,13,Fcompleting their rounds.
