OL,7,FThe council told ITV News that the
OL,8,F"original collective grievance,
OL,9,Fsubmitted in June 2023, did not
OL,10,Finclude any allegations of bullying
OL,11,Fand mismanagement. The collective
OL,12,Fgrievance specifically cited finishing
OL,13,Fon time, size of rounds and said that
OL,14,Fit sought consistency in the way leave
OL,15,Fwas allocated."
