OL,7,FA GMB spokesman said: "GMB members are
OL,8,Fextremely disappointed that we have
OL,9,Fnot been given a copy of the
OL,10,Findependent report that we were
OL,11,Fpromised, instead we've been given a
OL,12,Fwhitewashed report written by the Head
OL,13,Fof Service, Stuart Wright, who in our
OL,14,Fview is biased and not impartial.
OL,16,F"We've also had no contact or offers
OL,17,Ffrom South Tyneside Council to meet to
OL,18,Fresolve the dispute so the action goes
OL,19,Fahead this week again.
