OL,7,F"We have been told if we share the
OL,8,Freport with anyone they will deny us
OL,9,Fthe right to appeal against the
OL,10,Foutcomes of the Wright report."As the
OL,11,Faction we've taken seems not to have
OL,12,Ftriggered any response from management
OL,13,For the elected members of the ruling
OL,14,Fparty, we are now considering our next
OL,15,Fsteps and cannot rule out indefinite
OL,16,Faction being taken in the near future."
