OL,7,FThe council responded to some of the
OL,8,Fallegations made by the GMB union by
OL,9,Fsaying it has "always been clear that
OL,10,Fthe independent investigation report
OL,11,Fwould be considered by the Director of
OL,12,FPlace and Communities in reaching his
OL,13,Fdecision on whether the grounds of the
OL,14,Fgrievance are upheld, and this
OL,15,Freflected the applicable council
OL,16,Fpolicies. That report was considered,
OL,17,Fand the outcome of the Director's
OL,18,Freport was shared with Trade Unions
OL,19,Fand each of the individuals involved
OL,20,Fin the grievance in January 2024."
